NAME
    Encode::IBM - IBM-specific encoding mappings

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.06 of Encode::IBM, released September
    25, 2007.

SYNOPSIS
        use Encode;
        use Encode::IBM;
        binmode( STDIN, ':encoding(ibm-835)' );
        binmode( STDOUT, ':encoding(ibm-947-sosi)' );

DESCRIPTIONS
    This module provides encoding extensions of IBM-specific mappings. The
    sources are from the ICU mapping repository:

        http://oss.software.ibm.com/cvs/icu/charset/data/ucm/

ENCODINGS
        ibm-835
        ibm-937
        ibm-939
        ibm-947

        ibm-835-sosi
        ibm-939-sosi
        ibm-947-sosi

SEE ALSO
    Encode

